title: Indonesia : mobile phone internet users 2017 to 2023
yAxis: Number of mobile phone internet users in millions
summary: Overall Number of mobile phone internet users in millions has increased over the Year.
Number of mobile phone internet users in millions is slightly increasing from 2018 to 2023.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2018 and 2019.
Maximum Number of mobile phone internet users in millions, about 100.4 was reported at Year 2023
Minimum Number of mobile phone internet users in millions about 79.7 was reached at Year 2018
